N filelist.pkg
D  5 Feb 2025
U 7
d 'FILELIST': module to recursively search directories for files
d 
d   filelist searches a directory for files that match a specific
d pattern and continues searching recursively in all its
d subdirectories. Search results either replace the data in memory
d or are saved as a Stata dataset on disk. The results include the
d file size in bytes.
d 
d KW: data management
d KW: directory
d KW: file
d KW: recursive
d 
d Requires: Stata version 9.2
d 
d Distribution-Date: 20190518
d 
d Author: Robert Picard
d Support: email picard@@netbox.com
d 
f f\filelist.ado
f f\filelist.sthlp
e
